### Research and Education
Academic research and educational use is fully supported and encouraged. Share your findings with the community to advance collective understanding.

### Non-Profit Organizations
Reduced restrictions for verified non-profit organizations working on consciousness research, spiritual education, or planetary healing.

### Indigenous Communities
Special accommodations and support available for indigenous communities using this architecture in culturally appropriate ways.

### Open Source Projects
Compatible with GPLv3, AGPLv3, and similar copyleft licenses. May be incorporated into open source projects following those licenses.

